{"tid":2480544,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【真理比生命更重要】《關於地球的運動》討論區","createTime":"2021-04-08T15:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T06:52:27.000Z","uid":74339,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f8e431e8e3e86a27bc07da226fe49d48aaabca3","tid":2480544,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-08T15:06:21.000Z","msg":"故事背景簡介：故事以15世紀的歐洲作為背景，羅馬天主教以外，或者質疑上帝創世論都會被當作異端思想，不斷被處以火刑的時代。主角神童拉法爾已經預定好了要跳級上大學，而大家也都期待他去專攻當時最為重要的神學。對於最為重視合理性的拉法爾而言這是必然的選擇，只要遵循合理性世界就是易如反掌的。然而某一天，在拉法爾的身邊出現的神秘男人，他所研究的正是在異端思想中最核心的「真理」，地動說。<br />\n<br />\n全集link： <a href=\"https://www.mangabz.com/19285bz/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mangabz.com%2F19285bz%2F&d=VcdoNmHqL8UCHTV4lpGTbYE4T4y%2BYV5jPOnVoTo%2FPYs%3D&h=bd153ef9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mangabz.com/19285bz/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeFEd3CVp5fMa8WzR5CPiTT6dn6ezF6tCZpy8Ky9DPdw3?filename=xy1s4Jz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxy1s4Jz.jpg&h=4e9107dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmufDxZonAitzsRY2TEAcfUHKnMN2i2mqgWPcbn3txVV?filename=AgXG9ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAgXG9ad.jpg&h=b4d3cc93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPPVeLTF5P4rvwj7PqcJVZv1wDazWVH7dNCHjJe1pB73s?filename=kCsDrWS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCsDrWS.jpg&h=9c7f492f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAGOZ7n.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAGOZ7n.png&h=7c269b06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdWEKy2YDFTs45bk5QLCqo5Mhqv7PBzcrTmMujz6X1qng?filename=vnJqhT5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvnJqhT5.png&h=0bc0499e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi